\v 22 Ophangisa\x + 28.20.\x* ukunotha\x + 20.21. Hlab. 30.7.\x* ungumuntu olelihlo elibi\x + 23.6. Dute. 15.9.\x*, njalo engazi ukuthi ubuyanga buzamehlela\x + 22.16.\x*.
