\v 25 Ongasuthisekiyo\x + 13.10.\x*\x + Hlab. 101.5.\x* udunga ingxabano\x + 15.18.\x*, kodwa othemba eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uzakhuluphaliswa\x + 11.25. 1 Tim. 6.6.\x*.
